{"tid":1869044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家係宣揚港獨嘅最佳時機","createTime":"2020-02-08T02:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T09:15:47.000Z","uid":336524,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ffc07bccf0ec142b934747cce5b73772712593","tid":1869044,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"政府嘅腐敗無能上升到一個最戇鳩嘅點。<br />\n然而我地無辦法制約呢班政府高層，因為佢地係受命於中央，而唔係受命於民。<br />\n我地無普選，特首先會咁放肆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n我要普選，還政於民！<br />\n沒有普選，唯有獨立！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a703071f1e79ffeacb49032242b80837c5036f91","tid":1869044,"uid":336524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"一切嘅根源在於我地無能力制約呢個政府。<br />\n我地必須要有普選或者獨立。<br />\n然而，呢個中共好明顯唔會比普選我地。<br />\n我地唔能夠戇鳩鳩咁等中共比普選我地，咁同白等黑警被清算一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立，唯一出路！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5241aebe10dfb7288590b5cc0f42dff4eb1754b","tid":1869044,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"令我諗起呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【除左水＆蔬菜】香港一早糧食獨立左啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1865466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1865466</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以前一提起港獨個個都話冇可能，今次中国肺炎正正證明咗，中国只係香港既負累！勁多帶病毒既人入晒嚟香港！同時香港係唔使靠中国都得！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2d9afb04ff1d35e00dff6b2dd965dd29cd5cda","tid":1869044,"uid":336524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"我相信只要宣傳得好<br />\n今次可以拉埋唔少阿叔師奶撐港獨<br />\n好想快啲出去貼連儂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6de227918e6770b628fed8f0f986d7074ed552b","tid":1869044,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5241aebe10dfb7288590b5cc0f42dff4eb1754b","